{"tid":2052484,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"歷史上有冇邊個球員嘅頭幾場波勁得過洛迪高高斯","createTime":"2020-06-05T14:29:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-12T12:12:08.000Z","uid":199081,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"7ba7f9a19fb6ea032afb8c3434b8d230a8c23e74","tid":2052484,"uid":199081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T14:29:49.000Z","msg":"上季有個雲尼素斯 佢扭波好睇係幾好睇 但唔識傳中唔識射波 <br />\n然後睇球皇片洛迪高嘅技術仲平庸過雲尼素斯<br />\n所以好多皇迷都覺得佢會差過雲尼素斯<br />\n<br />\n結果洛迪高<br />\n第一場熱身賽對拜仁入球靚罰球<br />\n第一場西甲後備上陣93秒就入波 破埋當年真朗嘅紀錄<br />\n第一場歐聯正選就完美帽子戲法<br />\n填滿咗皇馬上半季嘅右翼大洞<br />\n<br />\n雖然唔係真係佢生涯嘅頭幾場波 但喺豪門嘅登場有冇邊個夠佢勁"},{"pid":"cb7d86eebca02735607b501014ff58926449e7f7","tid":2052484,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T14:33:55.000Z","msg":"奧斯卡 踢車第一場歐聯打祖記 兩粒世界波梅開二度"},{"pid":"ed3e9d5936b23765dbbb8af1aef7993d21b0a0a2","tid":2052484,"uid":10392,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T14:34:12.000Z","msg":"拉舒福特？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A4gyZzm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA4gyZzm.jpg&h=173826b7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"254e48723948341cd5875016f9a8e89ed063813e","tid":2052484,"uid":3135,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T15:07:51.000Z","msg":"朗隊歐聯debut入三粒仲有初出道射爆阿仙奴"},{"pid":"a225880101f7dad938c77f317031123f064c439a","tid":2052484,"uid":301653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T15:09:50.000Z","msg":"下半季一開始已經收咗皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔知已經俾拖舟雪咗幾耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48195e3baeb5631876a40086f4ad1a92b36524d5","tid":2052484,"uid":12034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T15:10:35.000Z","msg":"馬迪爾<br />\n馬捷達<br />\n拉什福特"},{"pid":"55e71470a3e8b8d2f4af0e38fa2a74d2d74ed84a","tid":2052484,"uid":42740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":